{"tid":814924,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想買哥基，有無狗場推薦？（唔要領養）","createTime":"2018-09-11T15:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T03:18:26.000Z","uid":145847,"like":32,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"feee8ad7610f1cb910f285025e51afc8b80087d4","tid":814924,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"我知肯定會有領養撚<br />\n我都知被遺棄嘅狗好可憐<br />\n同樣地，狗場嘅狗到一定年齡都無人要一喺做種狗、一喺人道毀滅，一樣可憐<br />\n所以我本著大愛精神決定唔歧視狗場狗，去狗場買隻陪伴我<br />\n但想問吓邊間狗場好？求巴打指教"},{"pid":"445a404bb03442b3e96ed51e574152c43df92c4f","tid":814924,"uid":40272,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"啲義工好撚麻撚煩 你選擇好明智"},{"pid":"b9cd49598eb7dd030e4119547a91fde4c646a004","tid":814924,"uid":2419,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"你頂住 我走先"},{"pid":"c505c3d16c0ddbb1757c9a9d9630527e462f697d","tid":814924,"uid":58247,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"領養撚屌咪撚入黎搞樓主 唔係既話我屌到你地老母反白眼"},{"pid":"1f0b74355fa2aefabba2fcd18d0e5491f10c7880","tid":814924,"uid":54904,"like":8,"dislike":46,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"自認仆街咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你仲可以講到咁冠冕堂皇<br />\n比人屌都唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ce1d65c07214d525acd724fd53fdd5608751e8","tid":814924,"uid":46323,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"領養義工批得黎<br />\n樓主買個隻狗都已經3歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9cb499def48dcea65019bae96ae17e6818528c","tid":814924,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知肯定會有領養撚<br />\n我都知被遺棄嘅狗好可憐<br />\n同樣地，狗場嘅狗到一定年齡都無人要一喺做種狗、一喺人道毀滅，一樣可憐<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">我本著大愛精神決定唔歧視狗場狗</span>，去狗場買隻陪伴我<br />\n但想問吓邊間狗場好？求巴打指教</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗撚就係咁虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"a865912f7a62f94113feda71dce0525db5381d0f","tid":814924,"uid":151664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"想買隻白色松鼠狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80f725a58ca67e6da1f7eda2ae87a9ef9645439","tid":814924,"uid":145847,"like":31,"dislike":5,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自認仆街咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你仲可以講到咁冠冕堂皇<br />\n比人屌都唔抵可憐[img]assets/faces/dog/haha.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n我喺一個仆街，我只喺想要隻竉物狗，又唔知領養返尼嘅狗前主人有無虐待佢搞到有陰影，又要比狗義工煩。<br />\n你滿口仁義道德，但歧視狗場狗，忽視狗場狗現實慘況，以助長狗場為由拒絕向年幼就離開母犬嘅犬b伸出援手，你與我無異，只是比我更冠冤堂皇"},{"pid":"4a8696125822657010712c4be337d6a6e6c6a109","tid":814924,"uid":145847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"講返正題,有無邊間狗場大家買過又覺得好"},{"pid":"eaeacc1f0282e8eb642ec6fa5cb6c0808cf700bd","tid":814924,"uid":3253,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"領養過，仲有比一筆錢<br />\nD狗義工一，二個星期上黎家訪一次<br />\n仲要經常唔通知情況突然間<br />\n然後每日都問你狗嘅情況，叫我比相做證明<br />\n維持左幾個月近半年最後真係頂唔順退翻俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8316f6ad4d835ea6d97a90b0d6fee8176de7ab0c","tid":814924,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57642fef04430f5c110d17b4074f8e2714a28342","tid":814924,"uid":83609,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"越多人買咪越助長更多不人道繁殖<br />\n<br />\n想買咪買囉樓主，唔需要滿口歪理去撐自己買狗理由架"},{"pid":"4450c0212bb8600ac5ef6107668849dc9ac23528","tid":814924,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"狗場買要